00:34:16,20 --> 00:34:22,83
- 你需要钱吗？ - 我好想念你
- Do you need money? - I miss you so much.

289
00:34:25,16 --> 00:34:27,04
罗悌 ...
Lotte ...

290
00:34:27,66 --> 00:34:31,70
罗悌 ...不要再与我联络了
Lotte ... Do not contact me again.

291
00:34:49,00 --> 00:34:52,95
- 你看来累坏了 - 谢谢
- You look tired. - Thank you.

292
00:34:55,79 --> 00:34:59,91
- 有什么事吗？ - 没
- Is there something? - No.

293
00:35:00,08 --> 00:35:03,54
- 你工作是不是很辛苦？ - 是的，一点点
- Is there a lot going at work? - Yes, a little.

294
00:35:03,54 --> 00:35:07,12
我今天与探路者开会  还有柯乐斯格雷夫
I had a meeting with Pathfinder today. And Clas Greve.

295
00:35:07,29 --> 00:35:10,33
- 你没事吧？ - 没
- Are you Okay? - No.

296
00:35:12,54 --> 00:35:15,66
- 他没有录取吗？ - 绝对不会录取
- He does not get the job? - Absolutely not.

297
00:35:15,83 --> 00:35:19,12
明天我会打电话给其他仲介
Tomorrow I'll call the other agencies.

298
00:35:19,12 --> 00:35:23,08
我要确保他在挪威找不到任何工作
I will ensure that he does not get a job in Norway.

299
00:35:23,08 --> 00:35:25,66
为什么？
Why?

300
00:35:25,66 --> 00:35:29,66
你找到你的手机了吗？
Did you find your mobile, by the way?

301
00:35:29,66 --> 00:35:32,54
- 你的手机不是丢了 - 找到了
- You had lost your mobile. - Yes.

302
00:35:32,70 --> 00:35:35,29
- 在画廊？ - 没错
- At the Gallery? - Yes.

303
00:35:35,29 --> 00:35:39,83
- 好 再喝一杯？ - 好，谢谢你
- Well. More wine? - Yes, thank you.

304
00:36:42,75 --> 00:36:45,24
奥雅纳？
Ove?

305
00:36:45,25 --> 00:36:50,04
奥雅纳 ...
Ove ...

306
00:38:13,12 --> 00:38:16,20
- 嗨 - 你怎么跑来了？
- Hey. - What are you doing here?

307
00:38:18,54 --> 00:38:21,74
你进来好久，却没有出来
You went down here, and did not come out.

308
00:38:21,75 --> 00:38:24,37
- 我很担心 - 担心什么？
- I was worried. - About what?

309
00:38:24,54 --> 00:38:27,79
没事
Nothing.

310
00:38:27,79 --> 00:38:31,33
- 罗杰 你... - 怎么？
- You Roger ... - Yes?

311
00:38:32,04 --> 00:38:35,12
祝你今天工作顺利，还有
Have a nice day at work, then.

312
00:38:51,00 --> 00:38:54,08
我爱你
I love you.

313
00:40:28,79 --> 00:40:31,87
奥雅纳！
Ove!

314
00:40:43,87 --> 00:40:48,87
- 奥雅纳，你住在哪里？ - 娜塔莎...
-Ove, where do you live? -Natasha ...

315
00:40:49,16 --> 00:40:51,99
奥雅纳 ...奥雅纳！
Ove ... Ove!

316
00:40:52,00 --> 00:40:54,58
你住在哪里... ？
Where do you live...?

317
00:41:10,04 --> 00:41:13,54
奥雅纳，你在车库发生了什么事？
Ove, what happened in the garage?

318
00:41:13,54 --> 00:41:16,62
你看到有人吗？
Did you see anyone?

319
00:41:21,58 --> 00:41:24,20
快回答我
Answer me now.

320
00:41:24,20 --> 00:41:28,79
你有看到发生了什么事吗？有别人吗？
Did you see what happened? Was there anyone there?

321
00:41:29,45 --> 00:41:32,54
- 娜塔莎... - 什么？
- Natasha ... - What?

322
00:41:38,75 --> 00:41:42,16
这到底是怎么回事？
What the hell is going on here?

323
00:42:04,95 --> 00:42:08,16
奥雅纳，密码是什么？
Ove, what is the password?

324
00:42:08,16 --> 00:42:10,83
- 保全的密码 - 娜塔莎...
- The password for the alarm. - Natasha ...

325
00:42:10,83 --> 00:42:14,45
我们要关掉保全警报 密码是什么？
We need to disable the alarm. What is the password?

326
00:42:14,45 --> 00:42:19,62
- 密码是什么！ - 我说的就是密码！是娜塔莎！
- What is my password! - This is what I am saying! Natasha!

327
00:42:20,79 --> 00:42:23,54
是沙 还是 撒？
Sh or Ch?

328
00:42:37,08 --> 00:42:39,74
奥雅纳 ...
Ove ...

329
00:42:41,50 --> 00:42:46,24
奥雅纳，怎么回事？
Ove, how's it going?

330
00:42:46,41 --> 00:42:50,08
- 怎么啦？ - 你坐到我车上的注射器
- What happened? - You sat on a syringe in the car.

331
00:42:50,08 --> 00:42:53,29
注射器？
A syringe?

332
00:42:53,29 --> 00:42:56,49
- 你很幸运了 - 幸运？！
- You have been lucky. - Lucky?!

333
00:42:56,50 --> 00:43:00,66
针头只碰到了你的膝盖 毒药没有完全渗透
You got the needle in the knee. The poison does not penetrate properly.

334
00:43:00,83 --> 00:43:04,41
- 是你任务搞砸了？ - 这是因为别的事！
- Have you fucked up? - This is about something else!

335
00:43:04,41 --> 00:43:07,62
戴安娜与 柯乐斯格雷夫有染
Diana has a relationship with Clas Greve.

336
00:43:07,62 --> 00:43:13,74
他要杀了你，因为他想上你的老婆！
He doesn't kill you because he is fucking your wife!

337
00:43:17,33 --> 00:43:22,87
- 那，快报警！ - 不能让警察发现这里！
- Call 112, then! - We shall have no police up here!

338
00:43:23,41 --> 00:43:27,66
拜托，罗杰 我需要去医院
Please, Roger. I need to go to the hospital.

339
00:43:27,66 --> 00:43:31,16
- 否则，我死定了 - 我去拿牛奶
- Otherwise, I die. - I'll get the milk.

340
00:43:31,16 --> 00:43:37,37
牛奶会中和毒物 他们在医院也只会做这个
Milk neutralizes poison. They would have done nothing else in the hospital.

341
00:43:53,79 --> 00:43:56,41
- 打电话！ - 别做傻事
- Call. - Do not do anything stupid.

342
00:43:56,58 --> 00:43:59,66
那我自己打
Then I do it myself.

343
00:44:01,66 --> 00:44:04,74
现在，我们都冷静下来 ...
Now we take it very quietly ...

344
00:45:48,00 --> 00:45:51,49
罗杰 我要和你谈谈
Roger. I have to talk to you.

345
00:46:27,62 --> 00:46:33,16
<i>我花了我大半辈子在追踪人</i>
I have spent most of my adult life tracking down people.

346
00:46:34,25 --> 00:46:37,33
<i>..微型发报机</i>
Microscopic transmitters.

347
00:48:27,20 --> 00:48:30,16
你好 我想要去小屋
Good day. Have thought of taking a short trip to the cottage.

348
00:48:30,37 --> 00:48:33,58
- 我还以为是奥雅纳 - 不是
- I thought it was Kjikerud. - No.

349
00:48:33,58 --> 00:48:37,33
- 这是他的车 - 没错
- It is his car. - Yes.

350
00:48:38,75 --> 00:48:44,54
- 你不是那些商人之一吗？ - 我被炒鱿鱼了
- Aren't you one of those businessmen? - I got fired.

351
00:48:44,54 --> 00:48:48,79
- 我可以把车停在谷仓吗？ - 每天500元
- Can I put the car in the barn? - 500 per day.

352
00:48:48,79 --> 00:48:52,62
你随便停在路旁就不用钱了
You can get free down the road, you know.

353
00:49:01,62 --> 00:49:07,66
如果你要用拖拉机的话，要另外收费！
If you drive the tractor, then I want compensation!

354
00:49:35,54 --> 00:49:41,54
- 私人土地 进去要钱喔！ - 我只是要找罗杰布朗
- the amount of legwork here today! - I'm just going to visit Roger Brown.

355
00:49:41,70 --> 00:49:46,66
- 要找那个商人？ - 没错
- Is he a businessman? - Yes.

356
00:49:46,66 --> 00:49:50,08
- 要找他做什么呢？ - 我们要谈个交易
- What are you doing with him? - We have a deal.

357
00:49:50,08 --> 00:49:54,33
你们要做什么，我都没有意见，但是...
I have nothing to do with what you are doing, but ...

358
00:49:54,33 --> 00:49:57,99
他们租的小木屋 使用人不包括你喔
He has not invited you for coffee and cakes at the cabin.

359
00:49:58,16 --> 00:50:00,54
租的小木屋？
At the cabin?

360
00:50:00,54 --> 00:50:08,83
由于它是我的财产，你要使用也要付钱
Since it is my property, some compensation is perhaps reasonable.

361
00:53:23,75 --> 00:53:25,79
去搜索！
Search!

362
00:55:17,20 --> 00:55:20,29
哈罗？
Hello?

363
00:58:33,54 --> 00:58:36,33
你是谁？
Who are you?

364
00:58:36,33 --> 00:58:39,20
哦，哦天啊 ...
Oh, oh hell ...

365
00:59:46,54 --> 00:59:49,37
你不该起来！
You should not stay up!

366
00:59:50,20 --> 00:59:54,91
- 有没有人问起我？ - 没有，过来躺下
- Has anyone asked for me? - No. Come and lie down again.

367
00:59:54,91 --> 00:59:59,41
除了警察 他们坐在在走廊上等你醒来
Apart from the police. They are sitting waiting for you in the hallway.

368
01:00:00,66 --> 01:00:04,37
我说等你吃过早餐再说
I said you should eat breakfast first.

369
01:00:27,29 --> 01:00:32,58
因为你可能面临情况 ...你擅长搏斗吗？
Because if you manage to turn into ....., are you good at fighting.

370
01:00:32,58 --> 01:00:35,08
有听说过升龙拳吗？
Ever heard of co-daw-ying?

371
01:00:35,08 --> 01:00:41,74
没有吧 你知道世上有多少种武术吗？ 三千种
Not so strange.Do you know how many martial arts there? 3000.

372
01:01:08,91 --> 01:01:11,66
埃及的武术 ...
Egyptian martial arts ...

373
01:01:21,95 --> 01:01:24,16
站住
Stand still!

374
01:01:24,33 --> 01:01:28,45
松代，我逮到他了！
Sunded, I got him!

375
01:01:28,66 --> 01:01:31,33
我是奥拉夫 松代, 犯罪调查局的
Olav Sunded from NCIS.

376
01:01:31,50 --> 01:01:35,16
你涉嫌谋杀农民 辛得勒
You are suspected of murdering of the farmer Sindre Aa.

377
01:01:35,16 --> 01:01:39,99
奥雅纳先生，跟我们进去休息
Join us Kjikerud, we will rest inside.

378
01:01:40,62 --> 01:01:43,83
你是奥雅纳没错吧？
You are Ove Kjikerud?

379
01:01:43,83 --> 01:01:45,95
没错
Yes.

380
01:02:06,62 --> 01:02:10,91
- 我们要去哪里？ - 要带你回警署问话
- Where are we? - Elverum Police Station for questioning.

381
01:02:10,91 --> 01:02:14,95
希望您能合作，这样我明天才可以去奥斯陆
Hope you cooperate, so I can go to Oslo tomorrow.

382
01:02:14,95 --> 01:02:20,49
- 所有的巡逻车请注意 - 他们两个也希望你合作
- Notice to all patrol cars. - Both of them, in other words.

383
01:02:20,50 --> 01:02:22,66
B30 回报. 请说状况
Bravo 3-0 answers.

384
01:02:22,66 --> 01:02:25,83
卡尔森来报案 他的卡车失窃
Egmon Karlsen has reported his truck stolen.

385
01:02:25,83 --> 01:02:29,87
- 卡尔森的声音听起来是清醒的吗？ - 不像，没很清醒
- Did Karlsen sound like he was sober? - Not entirely, no.

386
01:02:29,87 --> 01:02:34,95
打给巴姆斯酒吧 他可能停在那忘了
Call Bamse pub. It is probably parked there.

387
01:02:35,29 --> 01:02:40,58
- 你为什么要杀那个农民呢？ - 我不知道你在说什么
- Why did you murder the farmer, then? - I have no idea what you're talking about.

388
01:02:40,58 --> 01:02:43,79
你把宾士车停在他的谷仓
Your Mercedes was in Sindre Aa's barn.

389
01:02:43,79 --> 01:02:47,62
- 然后把他的拖拉机开进山沟里 - 我从来没有听说过他的名字
- You drove his tractor into the ditch. - I have never heard the name.

390
01:02:47,62 --> 01:02:53,54
- 巴姆斯酒吧外没有车 - 我现在有更重要的案子要办
-  No truck outside the Bamse pub. - I have more important things to do now.

391
01:02:53,54 --> 01:02:56,37
那去旗威酒吧外找！
Check behind the Kiwi.

392
01:02:56,37 --> 01:02:58,54
抱歉
Sorry.

393
01:02:58,54 --> 01:03:02,49
- 我们有几个证据 ... - 卡车在那，该死！
- We have several witnesses ... - There it is, of course, damn!

394
01:03:03,12 --> 01:03:09,45
打给卡尔森 我看到了卡车 我猜是他儿子偷开出来的
Call Egmon. I see the truck. Surely the son was the thief who borrowed it.

395
01:03:09,62 --> 01:03:13,12
你想做什么，兄弟？
What do you do now, Brugd?

396
01:03:18,75 --> 01:03:22,33
正如我刚说的 我们有很多的证据
As I said. We have much evidence.

397
01:03:22,50 --> 01:03:24,74
你无可抵赖的
And you flatly deny.

398
01:03:24,91 --> 01:03:30,62
请你告诉我那些，我们不清楚的细节
Then you tell me details, for I know nothing.

399
01:03:33,54 --> 01:03:37,41
农夫的邻居发现你倒在路边，拖拉机在山沟里
Aa's neighbor found you in the ditch next to the tractor.

400
01:03:37,41 --> 01:03:41,45
<i>我们开发了一种发胶，一小撮里就有上百个发报器</i>
We developed a gel that contained hundreds of transmitters per ml.

401
01:03:42,20 --> 01:03:45,41
<i>能附着任何物体，绝对不会脱落</i>
It sticks to everything, and is impossible to remove.

402
01:03:45,41 --> 01:03:47,83
我爱你
I love you.

403
01:03:53,25 --> 01:03:55,74
- 我们快离开 - 不行
- We have to leave. - No.

404
01:03:55,91 --> 01:04:01,54
他会杀了我们 他在我的头发上装了发报器！
He's going to kill us. He has smeared my hair with transmitters!

405
01:04:03,00 --> 01:04:07,49
- 冷静！ - 他在我的头发上装了发报器！
- Calm down! - He has smeared my hair with transmitters!

406
01:04:09,29 --> 01:04:12,83
- 他会杀了我！ - 冷静下来！
- He will kill me! - Calm down!

407
01:04:12,83 --> 01:04:15,91
我们一定要离开！
We must get out!

408
01:10:43,79 --> 01:10:46,99
你好，我是戴安娜
Hey, it's Diana.

409
01:10:47,00 --> 01:10:48,95
哈罗？
Hello?

410
01:10:48,95 --> 01:10:52,45
喂？罗杰，是你吗？
Hello? Roger, is that you?

411
01:11:30,66 --> 01:11:33,87
在这之后，我们去法医那
After this we go to Forensic.

412
01:11:33,87 --> 01:11:38,99
然后我们去看奥雅纳的房子
Then we take a look at Kjikerud's house

413
01:11:42,62 --> 01:11:47,16
“我是乡下来的女孩 ，你是挪威最性感的警察 ”
"I am a single girl from Gjovik. You are Norway's sexiest policeman. "

414
01:11:47,45 --> 01:11:53,58
“也是最聪明的，能碰个面吗？我随时有空 ”
"And the smartest. Will you meet me? I'm with the majority. "

415
01:12:06,66 --> 01:12:09,04
这里到底发生了什么事？
What the hell happened here?

416
01:12:16,50 --> 01:12:18,66
罗悌，等等 是我
Lotte, wait.

417
01:12:18,66 --> 01:12:24,87
- 你来这里做什么？发生了什么事？ - 我需要帮忙
- What are you doing here? What has happened? - I need help. Please.

418
01:12:27,66 --> 01:12:33,33
- 我不想连累到你 - 连累什么？
- I do not want to drag you into this. - Into what?

419
01:12:33,33 --> 01:12:38,49
他们问起时，不必说谎 就说，我来过
When they ask, do not lie. Just say that I was here.

420
01:12:41,04 --> 01:12:44,12
就说你是被我逼的
Just say that I forced myself in.

421
01:12:44,45 --> 01:12:47,91
发生了什么事？
What has happened?

422
01:12:47,91 --> 01:12:52,04
等着 我去拿东西来做清洁
Wait here. I'll get something to clean it with.

423
01:12:57,08 --> 01:13:00,33
你有没有剪刀？
Do you have a pair of scissors?

424
01:13:26,41 --> 01:13:29,54
罗悌，你在跟谁联络？
Lotte, who are you contacting?

425
01:13:29,70 --> 01:13:34,74
- 电话给我！ - 住手
- Give me the phone! - Stop.

426
01:13:34,75 --> 01:13:39,58
- “罗杰还活着，他在公寓 ” - 不是你想的那样...
- "Roger is alive. He is in the apartment." - It's not what you think ...

427
01:13:39,58 --> 01:13:44,95
- 这是怎么回事？ - 我也不知道！
- What is going on? - I do not know!

428
01:13:44,95 --> 01:13:48,20
- 这不是我的错！ - 这是怎么回事？
- It's not my fault! - What is going on?

429
01:13:48,20 --> 01:13:51,79
- 拜托你... - 格雷夫到底为什么找我？
- Please ... - What does Greve want with me?

430
01:13:51,79 --> 01:13:56,45
- 他想在‘探路者’工作 - 没有人会为求职杀人吧！
- He wants the job in Pathfinder. - You do not kill for a job!

431
01:13:56,45 --> 01:13:59,24
这关系到几十亿元
It's about billions.

432
01:13:59,25 --> 01:14:05,70
他们自从发现了探路者在找一个新经理人时，就努力在争取
They have been working with it since they found out Pathfinder is looking for a new manager.

433
01:14:05,87 --> 01:14:08,87
- “他们”是谁？！ - 柯乐斯
- Who are 'they'?! - Clas.

434
01:14:08,87 --> 01:14:12,16
- 他仍然在为‘贺得’工作 - 什么？
- He still works for HOTE. - What?

435
01:14:14,41 --> 01:14:18,70
- 什么？ - 他们有庞大的财政问题
- What?! - They have huge financial problems.

436
01:14:18,70 --> 01:14:23,04
美国人要求他们必须取得探路者的技术 才会金援
Amtech requires HOTE to provide them with Pathfinder technology.

437
01:14:23,04 --> 01:14:28,29
- 这就是柯乐斯的任务 - 你疯了吗？
- It was Clas' task. - Are you insane?

438
01:14:28,79 --> 01:14:33,74
我的任务是认识你，然后向你介绍他
I was going to teach you to recognize, and then introduce you to him.

439
01:14:33,91 --> 01:14:37,83
但是因为你不想见我了，他不得不改变计划
He had to make a new plan, because you did not want to see me anymore.

440
01:14:37,83 --> 01:14:40,91
他必须另外设法来认识你
He had to find a way to meet you.

441
01:14:42,70 --> 01:14:46,33
他的祖母有一张复制的鲁本斯油画
His grandmother had an old copy of a Rubens painting.

442
01:14:46,33 --> 01:14:51,58
他捏造了她跟德国军官的故事
He concocted a story about her getting it from a German officer.

443
01:14:51,75 --> 01:14:57,24
他把故事告诉戴安娜，她相信了
He told Diana the story and she believed him.

444
01:14:57,25 --> 01:15:00,04
然后，他遇见了你
Then he met you.

